oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: 5th Annual Roof-Top Ruckus
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Woodcuts (prints); Metal photoplates;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Two color window card (blue and red on white) announcing the 5th Annual Roof-Top Ruckus on July 4. Poster features woodcuts of stars and fireworks and a metal photoplate of the American flag.
